high_descs: Turn around and face the end of the white table where the trash can is.
Pick the white mug up from the table.
Go right and then left to face the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the mug out again.
Turn around and go right to stand in front of the blue coffee maker.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the table on your left.
Turn right and move to the front of the microwave on your left.
Warm the coffee mug in the microwave for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn around and move to the coffee maker on your right between the sink and the fridge.
Put the mug under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: place the mug to heat in the microwave and take it out
turn around to the coffee maker
place the mug under the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a hot mug under the coffee maker
